label: uncl5245
comment: Code qualifying the type of percentage.

values.label: Allowance
values.comment: (5044) Allowance expressed as a percentage.

values.label: Charge
values.comment: (5044) Charge expressed as a percentage.

values.label: Monetary amount adjustment percentage
values.comment: [5044] Specification of any additional charges, dues or deductions, expressed as a percentage.

values.label: Reinsurer's share
values.comment: To indicate the share of the reinsurer in a treaty.

values.label: Entry percentage
values.comment: To indicate the percentage used for the specified entry (e.g. commission %, deposits % ...).

values.label: Quality/yield
values.comment: (5482) The percentage of specified material in the total product.

values.label: Percentage of invoice
values.comment: Code specifying the percentage of invoice.

values.label: Reduction/surcharge percentage
values.comment: Percentage to calculate a reduction/surcharge.

values.label: Adjustment
values.comment: Code specifying the adjustment expressed as a percentage.

values.label: Bureau share
values.comment: London insurance market bureau (bureau share in reinsurance treaty).

values.label: Buffer stock requirement
values.comment: Anticipated additional consumption to safeguard against unforeseen shortages or demands.

values.label: Discount
values.comment: Discount expressed as a percentage.

values.label: Amount tolerance
values.comment: Tolerance of amount in percentage.

values.label: Percentage of note
values.comment: Percentage of debit or credit note.

values.label: Penalty percentage
values.comment: Code specifying the penalty percentage.

values.label: Interest percentage
values.comment: Code specifying the interest percentage.

values.label: Part of documentary credit amount
values.comment: Part of documentary credit amount in percentage subject to sight payment, deferred payment or acceptance when the documentary credit is available by mixed payment.

values.label: Percentage credit note
values.comment: Percentage of a credit note.

values.label: Percentage debit note
values.comment: Percentage of a debit note.

values.label: Percentage of insurance
values.comment: Code specifying the percentage of insurance.

values.label: Own risk percentage
values.comment: Percentage of total amount which is not covered by credit cover.

values.label: Transferred VAT percentage
values.comment: VAT percentage rate for which accountability is being transferred from one party to another. VAT means: Value added tax.

values.label: Part time employment
values.comment: The time a person is employed expressed as a percentage of the equivalent full time employment.

values.label: Voluntary contribution
values.comment: Contribution to a superannuation scheme which is not compulsory, expressed as a percentage of salary.

values.label: Attribute factor
values.comment: To indicate a mathematical factor, expressed as a percentage , used to multiply a specified attribute item.

values.label: Additional contribution
values.comment: Contribution to a scheme in addition to the normal contribution, expressed as a percentage (in superannuation usually expressed as a percentage of salary).

values.label: Benefits allocation
values.comment: Percentage of total benefits allocated to a person.

values.label: Attribute classification
values.comment: To indicate the percentage of a specified attribute classification (e.g. percentage contributed before a defined year for superannuation purposes).

values.label: Renegotiation trigger upper limit
values.comment: The percentage rise in a currency rate of exchange which would result in renegotiation of prices.

values.label: Renegotiation trigger lower limit
values.comment: The percentage fall in a currency rate of exchange which would result in renegotiation of prices.

values.label: Material reduction factor
values.comment: The percentage reduction in constituent material which occurs in the production process.

values.label: Acceptable price difference
values.comment: The maximum percentage increase or decrease resulting from price recalculation which will not result in price renegotiation.

values.label: Share of buyer's total requirement
values.comment: The percentage of the buyer's total acquisition requirement for the referenced or similar item which will be ordered from the named supplier.

values.label: Price increase
values.comment: The percentage increase in price of the referenced item since the last notification.

values.label: Share of tool cost paid by buyer
values.comment: The percentage of the cost of tooling which will be paid by the buyer.

values.label: Volume capacity usage
values.comment: Percentage of the volume capacity used.

values.label: Weight capacity usage
values.comment: Percentage of the weight capacity used.

values.label: Loading length capacity usage
values.comment: Percentage of the loading length capacity used.

values.label: Share of packaging cost paid by vendor
values.comment: The percentage of the cost of packaging which will be paid by the vendor.

values.label: Reduction percentage
values.comment: Reduction from an amount/price expressed in a percentage.

values.label: Surcharge percentage
values.comment: Additional amount expressed in a percentage.

values.label: Local content
values.comment: To indicate the percentage of a products local (i.e. domestic) content.

values.label: Chargeback
values.comment: Percentage amount charged back.

values.label: Gross turnover commission
values.comment: Percentage of gross turnover used to calculate commission.

values.label: Progress payment percentage
values.comment: Indicates the rate applying for a progress payment.

values.label: Offset
values.comment: Indicates the figure agreed between parties to calculate an offset.

values.label: Prepaid payment percentage
values.comment: A code to indicate the percentage of the prepayment.

values.label: Percentage of work completed
values.comment: A code to indicate the percentage of work completed.

values.label: Underwriting rating
values.comment: Table used for mortality or morbidity rating.

values.label: Mortgage interest rate
values.comment: Rate of interest used in amortization of a mortgage.

values.label: Maximum cost of living adjustment rate
values.comment: Maximum rate of the cost of living adjustment.

values.label: Humidity
values.comment: [6004] The amount of moisture in the air.

values.label: Minimum cost of living adjustment rate
values.comment: Minimum rate of a cost of living adjustment.

values.label: Contractor cost share
values.comment: The cost share borne by the contractor.

values.label: Government cost share
values.comment: The cost share borne by the Government.

values.label: Progress payment liquidation percentage
values.comment: The percentage applied to the liquidation of progress payments.

values.label: Fee percentage
values.comment: The percentage applied to determine the fee.

values.label: Resource availability
values.comment: Percentage of resource availability.

values.label: Resource efficiency
values.comment: Percentage of resource efficiency.

values.label: Rework yield
values.comment: Percentage yield from rework effort.

values.label: Gross profit margin
values.comment: Percentage calculated by dividing gross profit by net sales.

values.label: Remaining work
values.comment: Percentage of remaining work.

values.label: Actual work percent completed
values.comment: Percentage of actual work completed.

values.label: Earned value
values.comment: Percentage representing earned value.

values.label: Cost escalation
values.comment: Percentage of cost escalation.

values.label: Loss
values.comment: To identify the percentage of the loss.

values.label: Cost of living adjustment rate
values.comment: To specify a cost of living adjustment rate.

values.label: Percentage of due amount
values.comment: The percentage of an amount due.

values.label: Asset ownership
values.comment: Percent owned of an asset.

values.label: Common stock reported
values.comment: Percentage of common stock reported.

values.label: Preferred stock reported
values.comment: Percentage of preferred stock reported.

values.label: Ordinary profit to sales
values.comment: The ratio of ordinary profit to sales expressed as a percentage.

values.label: Invested capital ratio
values.comment: Ratio of invested capital to total capital.

values.label: Equity to loan ratio
values.comment: Ratio of equity to outstanding loans expressed as a percentage.

values.label: Equity to deposit ratio
values.comment: Ratio of equity to deposits expressed as a percentage.

values.label: Loan to deposit ratio
values.comment: Ratio of outstanding loans to deposits expressed as a percentage.

values.label: Percent of total
values.comment: Percentage of the total value.

values.label: Participation
values.comment: Participation expressed as a percentage.

values.label: Indebtedness
values.comment: Indebtedness expressed as a percentage.

values.label: Liquid ratio
values.comment: Ratio of liquid assets to current liabilities.

values.label: Net worth to total assets
values.comment: Ratio of net worth to total assets expressed as a percentage.

values.label: Subcontracted
values.comment: Percentage of work that is subcontracted.

values.label: Sales per employee
values.comment: Ratio of sales per employee expressed as a percentage.

values.label: Sales to net working capital
values.comment: Ratio of sales to net working capital expressed as a percentage.

values.label: Total liability to net worth
values.comment: Ratio of total liability to net worth expressed as a percentage.

values.label: Assets to sales
values.comment: Ratio of assets to sales expressed as a percentage.

values.label: Capital per employee
values.comment: Ratio of capital per employee expressed as a percentage.

values.label: Costs per employee
values.comment: Ratio of costs per employee expressed as a percentage.

values.label: Accounts payable to sales
values.comment: Ratio of accounts payable to sales expressed as a percentage.

values.label: Current liabilities to net worth
values.comment: Ratio of current liabilities to net worth expressed as a percentage.

values.label: Current liabilities to inventory
values.comment: Ratio of current liabilities to inventory value expressed as a percentage.

values.label: Current ratio
values.comment: Ratio of current assets to current liabilities expressed as a percentage.

values.label: Fixed assets to net worth
values.comment: Ratio of fixed assets to net worth expressed as a percentage.

values.label: Inventory turnover
values.comment: Net annual sales divided by inventory.

values.label: Quick ratio
values.comment: Ratio of cash and accounts receivable to current liabilities.

values.label: Resources retained for project
values.comment: The percentage of resources that must be retained for a project.

values.label: Return on assets
values.comment: Net profit after taxes divided by total assets.

values.label: Return on sales ratio
values.comment: Net profit after taxes divided by net annual sales.

values.label: Return on capital ratio
values.comment: Net profit after taxes divided by capital.

values.label: Shareholders' return ratio
values.comment: Net profit after taxes divided by net worth.

values.label: Contracts obtained by bid
values.comment: Percentage of contracts obtained by bid.

values.label: Contracts obtained by negotiation
values.comment: Percentage of contracts obtained by negotiation.

values.label: Cost plus basis
values.comment: Percentage of business conducted on a cost plus basis.

values.label: Lump sum payments
values.comment: Percentage of lump sum payments to total payments.

values.label: Purchases on letter of credit
values.comment: Percentage of purchases on letter of credit to total purchases.

values.label: Purchases on floor plan
values.comment: Percentage of purchases on floor plan basis to total purchases.

values.label: Change in sales
values.comment: Percentage change in sales.

values.label: Change in profit
values.comment: Percentage change in profit.

values.label: Damage
values.comment: Damage expressed as a percentage.

values.label: Interest on liabilities
values.comment: Paid finance cost divided by total liabilities.

values.label: Risk margin
values.comment: Total assets divided by interest on liabilities.

values.label: Liability ratio
values.comment: Ratio of liability to net worth expressed as a percentage.

values.label: Interest cover
values.comment: Paid finance cost divided by total income.

values.label: Change
values.comment: Change expressed as a percentage.

values.label: Expense
values.comment: Expenses expressed as a percentage.

values.label: Market share
values.comment: Share of the market business held by an entity.

values.label: Owned by small shareholders
values.comment: Percentage of an entity that is owned by small shareholders.

values.label: Paid in capital
values.comment: Percentage of capital paid in by shareholders.

values.label: Previous participation
values.comment: Previous participation expressed as a percentage.

values.label: Fixed fee
values.comment: Fixed fee expressed as a percentage.

values.label: Asset turnover
values.comment: Net annual sales divided by total assets.

values.label: Percentage of total payment
values.comment: A percentage based on a total payment.

values.label: Territorial trade percent
values.comment: Territorial trade expressed as a percentage.

values.label: Change in taxable income
values.comment: Change in the taxable income from one period to another.

values.label: Sales by type of customer
values.comment: Percentage of sales by type of customer.

values.label: Previous period percent of total
values.comment: The percent of the total from a preceding period.

values.label: Minority interest return on equity
values.comment: The return on equity achieved by a minority interest in an entity.

values.label: Change in ordinary income
values.comment: Change in ordinary income from one period to another.

values.label: Net sales to fixed assets
values.comment: The ratio of net sales to fixed assets expressed as a percentage.

values.label: Total liabilities to total assets
values.comment: The ratio of total liabilities to total assets expressed as a percentage.

values.label: Profit percentage
values.comment: The percentage applied to determine the profit.

values.label: Contractor above cost share
values.comment: The percentage of the cost over-run incurred by the contractor.

values.label: Contractor below cost share
values.comment: The percentage of the cost under-run allocated to the contractor.

values.label: Current liabilities to total liabilities
values.comment: Ratio calculated by dividing current liabilities by total liabilities expressed as a percentage.

values.label: Current assets to total liabilities
values.comment: Ratio calculated by dividing current assets by total liabilities expressed as a percentage.

values.label: Vessel experience factor
values.comment: The compilation of the total calculated volume vessel measurements, adjusted for on-board quantity or remaining on-board quantity, compared with the total calculated volume shore measurements expressed as a percentage.

values.label: Vessel load ratio
values.comment: The total calculated volume by vessel measurement upon sailing, less on-board quantity, divided by the total calculated volume by shore measurement at loading expressed as a percentage.

values.label: Vessel discharge ratio
values.comment: The total calculated volume by vessel measurement on arrival, less remaining on board, divided by the total calculated volume by shore measurement discharge expressed as a percentage.

values.label: National average percentile
values.comment: Relative ranking for a corresponding class to the national average.

values.label: Industry average percentile
values.comment: Relative ranking for a corresponding class to the industry average.

values.label: Non-current assets to net worth
values.comment: The ratio of non-current assets to net worth expressed as a percentage.

values.label: Non-current assets to total assets
values.comment: The ratio of non-current assets to total assets expressed as a percentage.

values.label: Sales to current assets
values.comment: The ratio of sales to current assets expressed as a percentage.

values.label: Working capital to sales
values.comment: The ratio of working capital to sales expressed as a percentage.

values.label: Creditors to sales costs
values.comment: The ratio of creditors to sales costs expressed as a percentage.

values.label: Concentration
values.comment: Concentration expressed as a percentage value.

values.label: Percentage of months before an instalment
values.comment: The number of months before an instalment is made expressed as a percentage.

values.label: Accounts receivable turnover
values.comment: Net annual sales divided by accounts receivable.

values.label: Employee costs to value added ratio
values.comment: Ratio of employee costs to total income minus raw materials and sales costs expressed as a percentage.

values.label: Interest payable to net sales ratio
values.comment: Ratio of interest payable divided by net sales expressed as a percentage.

values.label: Inventory to cost of goods sold ratio
values.comment: Ratio of inventory divided by cost of goods sold expressed as a percentage.

values.label: Liquid assets to sales ratio
values.comment: Ratio of liquid assets divided by net sales expressed as a percentage.

values.label: Return on value added ratio
values.comment: Ratio of total income minus raw materials and services to net sales expressed as a percentage.

values.label: Daily working capital need
values.comment: The value of working capital divided by net sales multiplied by 360.

values.label: Financial expenses to net sales ratio
values.comment: The ratio of financial expenses to net sales expressed as a percentage.

values.label: Inflation
values.comment: Percentage representing a general increase in prices and fall in the purchasing value of money.

values.label: Probability of financial distress
values.comment: The probability of financial distress expressed as a percentage.

values.label: Gearing
values.comment: Ratio of the total short and long term loans divided by shareholder equity expressed as a percentage.

values.label: Nestable percentage
values.comment: Extent expressed as a percentage to which an item can be nested within an identical item.

values.label: Data reliability percentage
values.comment: To identify the degree of the reliability of the data.

values.label: Transport weight completed
values.comment: The percentage of a transport weight that has been completed.

values.label: Transport volume completed
values.comment: The percentage of a transport volume that has been completed.

values.label: Percentage of order
values.comment: Percentage of an order.

values.label: Mutually defined
values.comment: As agreed by the trading partners.
